title: 193 - Bill Spent 37 Thousand Pounds on WHAT??????
description: Today’s episode of The POD kicks off with Ty Schmit leading the way, as the boys discuss their eventful weekend surviving a monstrous tornado. Before the boys jump into the Pod FOD, Bill informs the squad that he has finally moved into his NEW HAUSE! The boys then jump into the POD Fod, which is a folder compiled of all things around the internet. Today FOD includes a Clash of Clans update, Golden globes predictions, an MIT end of the world prediction and much much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
